nodes.text: Trehla Keelo was a female Human who lived in Mos Eisley on Tatooine during the Galactic Civil War. She was acquainted with Mayor Mikdanyell Guh'rantt, as well as with Vourk ver'Zremp, who was working in Jabba Desilijic Tiure's criminal empire, even if she did not appreciate Jabba the Hutt. Trehla Keelo used to try to be helpful to newcomers in Mos Eisley, since she considered the city a hive of scum and villainy. Vourk ver'Zremp would often refer new Jabba henchmen to her.
